{"tid":2488956,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"失業綜援申領個案增55% 觀塘深水埗元朗成重災區","createTime":"2021-04-14T14:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T15:12:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0aae34300b3bc3274e2886926c91b3dc075e833c","tid":2488956,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T14:59:25.000Z","msg":"政府去年6月設立限時1年的「援助失業人士特別計劃」，健全人士申請綜援的資產上限調高1倍，並豁免保險現金價值作資產等。社會福利署提交立法會特別財委會資料顯示，截至去年底，2020／21年度失業綜援個案按年上升55%約有1.95萬宗，當中約1.38萬宗屬新申請個案。<br />\n<br />\n申領失業綜援個案最多的地區依次為觀塘、深水埗及元朗，分別佔12.2%、12.1%及11.3%，跟上一個年度相若，最少是中西區及灣仔區，僅佔1.1%及1.2%。按職業劃分，逾9成失業綜援受助人是無業，部份人則任職雜工、清潔工人、送貨員及侍應生等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/ADKNHRE5AZB3XHJ432OEAYLIC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FADKNHRE5AZB3XHJ432OEAYLIC4%2F&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvmSJzKb80PJXVuqujnuB1ho%3D&h=7ed51cdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FADKNHRE5AZB3XHJ432OEAYLIC4%2F&h=52240cb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/ADKNHRE5AZB3XHJ432OEAYLIC4/</a>"},{"pid":"730c6632801279aaca6cf5856d044111bd54653c","tid":2488956,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:09:29.000Z","msg":"觀塘好撚多基層"},{"pid":"9ceced71cb3f1e879aa2fd77e3ad18c3350b069a","tid":2488956,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:12:47.000Z","msg":"深水埗好多人自己打疫苗"}]}